<title>USA: Inamed names Donald McGhan CEO.</title>
<headline>Inamed names Donald McGhan CEO.</headline>
<dateline>LAS VEGAS 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Inamed Corp said on Tuesday that Michael Farney resigned as director and chief executive officer, and Chairman Donald McGhan was named to the additional post of chief executive.</p>
<p>The comany said Jim McGhan was named president and director and will continue to serve as chief executive officer of its main subsidiary, McGhan Medical Corp.</p>
